            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> Both: Standard, HMO, Family Doctor, Telmed available</li>
              <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> Premium range: Moderate to high (similar across providers)</li>
              <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> Both: Excellent mobile apps and digital platforms</li>
              <li class="flex"><span class="text-primary-600 mr-2">•</span> Switching deadline: 30 November 2025 → 1 January 2026</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Provider Strengths</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
