          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Quick Answer: Sanitas vs SWICA Summary</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            Both are premium Swiss insurers offering comprehensive basic and supplementary coverage with excellent digital platforms. Sanitas provides modern app UX and flexible supplementary portfolio. SWICA excels in English support with dedicated line and generous wellness contributions (up to CHF 800/year). Choose Sanitas for digital-first experience, SWICA for service excellence and wellness benefits.
